    {
      "id": "n1",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 0,
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Paper-Based TestDaF Format, Tips and Practice"
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 1,
      "text": "The paper-based TestDaF has four separately assessed parts: Leseverstehen, Hörverstehen, Schriftlicher Ausdruck, and Mündlicher Ausdruck. The pure exam time is 3 hours and 15 minutes, with breaks between the parts. Tasks always relate to university and academic communication."
    },
    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "Pure exam time"
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 3,
      "text": "3h 15min"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 4,
      "text": "Result model"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
